Name: HELLPIT
About the game: Doomed to dungeon laden with traps, you are doomed to rot and die. It's up to you to be the first to escape the HELLPIT . A 3rd person platformer featuring many unique obstacles and traps. This game is balanced but don't be fool, this game can be hard and tricky. Key Features Simple mechanics - just hold W and jump Unique - No obstacles and traps layout are the same each time. Strategize - This is not straightforward game where you press 'W' key, You need to be good with your timing. Checkpoints - No save but checkpoints. Some obstacles are really hard to pass through. But when you made it, you feel like a boss. Hard but balanced - Unlike other rage game, this game designed is to be enjoyable challenge.
